  <brief_title>McGrath Videolaryngoscopy for Nasotracheal Intubation</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Comparison of McGrath Videolaryngoscopy and Macintosh Laryngoscopy for Routine Nasotracheal Intubation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
